31:41.274 --> 31:42.275
You're okay, though?

31:43.610 --> 31:44.694
Just at work.

31:45.111 --> 31:47.405
Just working late,
and I was thinking about you,

31:47.488 --> 31:48.823
and I want you to know...

31:51.409 --> 31:54.579
that I love you very much, kiddo, okay?

31:56.539 --> 31:57.999
I love you very much.

31:58.708 --> 32:00.418
You can go back to sleep now.

32:00.793 --> 32:01.836
Okay.

32:12.931 --> 32:15.767
You've reached
John Rayburn. Please leave a message.

32:15.850 --> 32:17.602
John, where the fuck are you, man?

32:17.685 --> 32:20.813
Come on. I've been calling you
all fucking night.

32:21.397 --> 32:22.857
You need to meet me, all right?

32:22.941 --> 32:25.276
You need to meet me,
like, right fucking now.

32:25.360 --> 32:27.654
What the fuck, man?
I don't know what to do, John.

32:27.737 --> 32:31.824
Come on, you gotta call me back, man.
I need you, I really fucking need you now.

32:32.408 --> 32:34.035
I wouldn't call if I didn't.

32:35.036 --> 32:37.205
So, call me back,
you fucking prick, come on.

32:37.622 --> 32:38.623
Call me back!

33:14.075 --> 33:15.368
What's gonna happen now?

33:17.829 --> 33:19.247
We're just gonna go forward.

33:20.832 --> 33:22.250
One foot follows the other.

33:23.376 --> 33:24.877
One day after another.

33:25.628 --> 33:27.797
How long is Danny gonna be
in the hospital for?

33:28.214 --> 33:29.424
He'll be home soon.

33:30.049 --> 33:32.010
And we'll have new guests and work to do.

33:32.093 --> 33:34.095
Mom, am I gonna have to answer
any more questions?

33:34.178 --> 33:36.973
Shh. You did good, Johnny.

33:39.017 --> 33:39.934
You all did.

33:40.643 --> 33:43.062
Now, shut your eyes
and try to get some sleep.

34:01.497 --> 34:02.331
You want?

34:02.790 --> 34:03.624
No.

34:05.835 --> 34:06.669
I gotta go.

34:08.880 --> 34:10.339
My cab's here. You want a ride?

34:10.423 --> 34:12.425
No, thank you.

34:12.508 --> 34:13.342
You sure?

34:13.426 --> 34:15.636
I'm gonna call... Mm.

34:16.554 --> 34:17.680
See you later.

34:28.066 --> 34:30.485
Attention, all passengers in the terminal:

34:30.568 --> 34:33.071
♪ Louis got Detroit
And Louis got Philly ♪

34:34.822 --> 34:37.617
♪ When's the last time you heard
