I was trying to think, but I, um...

35:09.357 --> 35:12.401
I couldn't hold onto anything, Mom,
and I, um...

35:15.571 --> 35:18.241
I couldn't even see.
Everything went black. I...

35:20.785 --> 35:23.996
I-I just-- I couldn't see anything.
Just-- just nothing.

35:24.330 --> 35:25.164
And, um...

35:27.667 --> 35:31.337
he turned to me, and he said
that all three of us were going to jail.

35:33.339 --> 35:37.009
I've been trying to call John all night,
and he's not answering my phone calls.

35:37.093 --> 35:39.470
And I don't know what to do,
so I came here.

35:40.888 --> 35:42.014
I don't know what to do.

35:45.059 --> 35:46.936
It's just so fucked up.

35:54.235 --> 35:55.153
Just...

35:57.822 --> 35:58.739
It is.

36:04.495 --> 36:07.331
Yes... it is.

36:10.126 --> 36:13.588
Marco was not getting it,
and he wasn't listening to me at all.

36:14.255 --> 36:16.257
I didn't know where else to go.
I came here.

36:27.101 --> 36:29.520
Come on. One drink won't hurt you.

36:30.897 --> 36:32.565
-Let's get some air.
-Yeah.

36:33.774 --> 36:36.360
Oh, you go ahead, I'm gonna get some ice.

36:37.445 --> 36:38.487
Okay.

37:06.974 --> 37:07.850
What are you doing?

37:08.184 --> 37:09.352
Mom, open the door.

37:09.435 --> 37:10.269
Mom!

37:11.020 --> 37:12.146
Oh, come on.

37:13.022 --> 37:14.065
Mom!

37:14.690 --> 37:15.816
Don't do this!

37:15.900 --> 37:16.734
Mom!

37:19.695 --> 37:20.988
Mom, open the door!

37:24.992 --> 37:27.411
You've reached the voicemail
of Detective Marco Diaz.

37:27.495 --> 37:30.039
If this is an emergency,
please hang up and dial 911.

37:30.122 --> 37:32.750
Otherwise, leave a message
and have yourself a safe day.

37:37.338 --> 37:38.172
I'm doing it.

37:39.215 --> 37:41.175
Meg, let me give you a ride home.

37:41.259 --> 37:43.427
-I'm--
-Give me a couple minutes.

37:43.803 --> 37:45.304
I need to go see him.

37:45.388 --> 37:47.640
-No, you need to go home.
-I need to go see him.

37:49.308 --> 37:51.185
Just wait right here
for a couple minutes.

37:51.269 --> 37:53.604
Home.

