Hello?

38:42.737 --> 38:45.239
John, I need you here.

38:46.574 --> 38:49.035
You've been avoiding
our calls all night. Stop it.

38:50.369 --> 38:52.121
You need to help the family.

38:52.747 --> 38:54.665
There's nothing more important than that.

38:55.541 --> 38:57.043
Come home right now.

38:58.753 --> 39:00.212
Tell me where you are.

39:01.547 --> 39:02.548
I can't.

39:02.923 --> 39:05.426
Yes, you can, and you fucking will.

39:06.010 --> 39:07.678
-Mom.
-How could you, John?

39:14.143 --> 39:15.895
I can't come home.

39:15.978 --> 39:18.272
John, how could you?

39:19.690 --> 39:21.275
How could you lie to me like that?

39:36.332 --> 39:39.251
-We lied.
-I don't want you to think of it that way.

39:39.335 --> 39:42.004
-Should've just went on the boat--
-You helped the family.

39:42.588 --> 39:44.965
-Should've went--
-Nothing's important than that.

39:45.049 --> 39:45.925
We lied.

39:46.008 --> 39:47.343
You helped the family.

39:47.927 --> 39:48.844
We lied.

40:07.488 --> 40:08.697
...door number 2.

40:08.781 --> 40:11.575
Attention, all passengers,
now boarding 134...

40:17.748 --> 40:18.666
Fuck it.

40:36.142 --> 40:38.978
134 passengers,
please board from door number...

40:53.409 --> 40:54.869
Hey, Kev, how's it hanging?

40:56.162 --> 40:57.246
You okay?

40:58.956 --> 41:00.875
-Kev?
-Yeah, yeah.

41:00.958 --> 41:02.293
-Uh...
-What's up?

41:02.376 --> 41:05.796
-Um, uh... I'm here...
-Oh, there's ice cream if you want.

41:05.880 --> 41:08.174
-to see if, uh, John...
-It's Scoonie's birthday.

41:08.257 --> 41:09.550
Is John here?

41:10.384 --> 41:11.218
No.

41:12.136 --> 41:13.596
- Hey, Scoonie?
- Hm?

41:13.679 --> 41:15.723
-You, uh, heard from Rayburn?
-Nope.

41:17.475 --> 41:19.143
But his mother called looking for him.

41:20.853 --> 41:21.687
Everything cool?

41:27.735 --> 41:30.196
Yeah, everything is-- Everything is good.

41:31.155 --> 41:31.989
Thanks.

41:35.618 --> 41:38.287
Hey, you ever read
The 48 Laws of Power? Huh?

41:39.246 --> 41:41.790
'Cause everybody in the joint
is so into that shit.

41:43.584 --> 41:46.003
Not me, man.
I can't get past the fourth law.

41:46.587 --> 41:49.924
You know what I mean?
Always say less than necessary.

41:50.466 --> 41:52.009
You know, you, you got that down.

