42:18.661 --> 42:20.829
Wanna get into it?
Come on, I'll pull it out.

42:23.123 --> 42:25.376
Fuck!

43:17.303 --> 43:19.263
I'm doing whatever I can to help him.

43:22.474 --> 43:23.309
Good.

43:24.351 --> 43:25.185
Thank you.

43:27.146 --> 43:30.149
So, we're all squared up, then?

43:30.608 --> 43:31.650
No, Roy.

43:33.152 --> 43:34.361
Not even close.

43:37.990 --> 43:39.700
You know what? Fuck you.

43:40.743 --> 43:43.996
You're losing everything 'cause you killed
your fucking brother, asshole.

43:49.084 --> 43:50.169
Go ahead.

43:50.252 --> 43:52.421
Anything to protect
the fucking Rayburn name.

43:53.380 --> 43:54.214
Right?

43:55.591 --> 43:58.177
...70 degrees.
Fort Myers...

44:01.513 --> 44:03.599
Oh, you fucked up but good, son.

44:05.726 --> 44:08.228
The way I see it,
you only have two options.

44:08.312 --> 44:09.938
One, you turn yourself in.

44:11.273 --> 44:13.817
That's a guaranteed outcome, checkmate.

44:14.860 --> 44:20.240
