there's no turning back.

45:07.538 --> 45:09.581
Yeah, John, this is Kevin again.

45:09.665 --> 45:11.583
Where the fuck are you, man? Um--

45:13.210 --> 45:16.004
John. Come on,
I need to talk to you.

45:16.422 --> 45:19.425
Call me back. Mom is fucking freaking out.
